  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078821\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"margin-top:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.78056 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c5a67ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIElPdV7nRXj2Ria0DGySgkekpFviaX8VQwaR4MGKJLfedCfdiakXmylnx3ZcHDOyLM4fmIlFCBPrnB2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文丨苏扬</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">编辑丨徐青阳</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果未来两年计划大幅扩展手机产品线，预计到2027年秋季，旗舰iPhone机型数量将从目前的5款增至至少7款。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此轮产品升级的核心是苹果首款折叠屏iPhone，预计将于2026年秋季正式发布。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士称，这款折叠设备在展开后形态更接近小型iPad，有望带来与传统智能手机不同的使用体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">另外，苹果计划于2027年秋季推出更具里程碑意义的iPhone 20周年纪念版。该机型将采用前后双曲面玻璃机身设计，实现真正的全面屏效果，屏幕将延伸至设备四边边缘，彻底消除传统黑色边框。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">01&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">站在十字路口的苹果</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果此次对iPhone产品线进行扩展与重塑，正值其面临市场增长压力的关键时期——行业普遍面临智能手机市场饱和、用户换机周期延长等挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果财报显示，其iPhone业务在2025财年实现了2090亿美元的年销售额，同比增长4%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-widget=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078820\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.86337 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"302\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=151ee18c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIElPdV7nRXj2Ria0DGySgkek7rf9Uib22aLMDpHDTVl4SajNX9IHCFJWjrpuwY5a1MKOaUibU8Q4f1Ww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);display: block;font-size: 12px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图：经历两年疲软期后，iPhone销量终于再次呈现出积极态势</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">分析普遍认为，这一增长主要得益于iPhone 17系列在外观设计上带来的显著变化，成功刺激了部分用户的换机需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，苹果的策略引发了不同观点讨论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有分析指出，苹果的新策略意图明确：通过折叠屏等高端创新产品提升平均售价与利润空间，同时以更具性价比的机型扩大用户基数和市场份额，最终实现全价位段的市场覆盖与整体增长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078819\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6986754966887417\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"604\" style=\"margin-top:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.43128 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"393\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c9706935&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIElPdV7nRXj2Ria0DGySgkek9ShVKrE5dVeeicTFJZ9Lb2FqfCDCLKUnWBdDWhREVLpvxcR9CLXciclg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，市场上也出现了批评的声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有观点认为，近年部分iPhone新款的升级聚焦于内部性能与零部件，而在整体设计和用户体验上缺乏突破性革新，这种策略被类比为“剃须刀更换刀片”——外部形态不变，仅对内部进行常规迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078817\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4653130287648054\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"591\" style=\"margin-top:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:2.14909 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"262\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e6bafc0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIElPdV7nRXj2Ria0DGySgkekRR2XrVpc35NibjHyHwILGoPpakpibiaQJaxhzef3Wicyk9nFEDYCXiaDb5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更有评论回溯历史，认为苹果已经逐渐背离了乔布斯时代“专注打造极致精品”的产品哲学。在当前由职业经理人主导、更注重财务指标（如平均售价）的运营模式下，产品线日趋复杂化，这或许在短期内能带来财务收益，但长期来看可能损害其以创新和简洁著称的品牌根基。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078818\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3993453355155483\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"611\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 277.141px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 2.5041 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e23f550c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIElPdV7nRXj2Ria0DGySgkekicZmhkAKsiaLiajKqnBqdH4W7egv2Ic1UdDeSIHgy7Ushzo0GnfQUuXHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论如何，从折叠屏的跨界探索到无边框的形态革命，苹果正试图通过一场密集的产品攻势，在竞争日益激烈、创新门槛不断提高的智能手机市场中，重新绘制增长曲线并回应各方的期待与质疑。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">02&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">两年发七款新机型寻求破局</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果路线图展现了该公司为打破市场僵局所制定的激进产品策略。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来两年内，苹果计划以罕见的高频节奏，发布覆盖从入门到顶尖、从传统到新形态的全系列机型，意图通过精准的市场分层与供应链革新重回高增长轨道。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体规划如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">1）2026年春季（1款）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">iPhone 17e：定位入门机型，首次为该系列加入磁吸无线充电功能，并搭载新一代自研调制解调器C1X，主打高性价比与基础体验升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">2）2026年秋季（2款）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">iPhone 18 Pro / Pro Max：旗舰系列迎来三项重要升级——屏下FaceID实现真正全面屏、机械光圈相机提升影像控制力、以及先进芯片封装技术强化端侧AI能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">iPhone Fold：苹果首款折叠屏手机，采用横向展开设计，形态接近小型iPad，外屏5.3英寸、内屏7.7英寸，代表苹果对折叠形态的差异化理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacin